IMMEDIATE
No. 55/4/CF-62
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 21st May 1962,
The undersigned is directed te state that
Shri C.R. Pattabhi Raman, Deputy Minister for Planning,
* has also been appointed as Deputy Minister in the Ministry
of Labour & Empleyment. His designation henceforward will
be Deputy Minister in the Ministry of Labour & Employment
and for Planning,
He assumed his new office with effect
from the afternoon tod ay, May 21, 1962,
( B.G. Rau )
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister/the Private Secretary to the Prime Minister, for
information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Presid ent/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
Redan
( B.G. Rau )
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additionai Secretaries to the Government of India/the Chairman,
Railway Board, for information,
Copy forwarded to all Ministries of the Government of
India/Department of Parliamentary Affairs/Planning Commission/
Department of Atomic Energy/Prime Minister's Secretariat/
Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for information.
( D.P. Chopra )
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
"MALHOTRA"
150 copies.
